        "previous_guid": "0A0616CC9A114270B7AA79865FE3811E",
        "section": "Prepare the reaction mix - volume per well is 10.5 \u03bcL for a 96-well plate.",
        "section_color": null,
        "section_duration": 0,
        "is_substep": false,
        "step": "Vortex the tube briefly to mix the components. Centrifuge the tube briefly to spin down the contents and to eliminate air bubbles from the solution.\n ",
